# Random Number Generator

A simple and customizable random number generator built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Generate random numbers within your specified range with various options for customization.

## 🚀 Features

- Generate random numbers within a custom range
- Option to include/exclude decimal numbers
- Copy results to clipboard
- Configurable number of results
- Instant generation with real-time validation
- Mobile-responsive design

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (ES6+)

## 📦 Installation

1. Clone the repository:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/random-number-generator.git
```

2. Navigate to the project directory:
```bash
cd random-number-generator
```

3. Open `index.html` in your web browser

## 💻 Usage

1. Enter your desired minimum and maximum values
2. Select whether you want decimal numbers or integers
3. Choose how many numbers you want to generate
4. Click the "Generate" button
5. Use the "Copy" button to copy results to clipboard
